steps.prompt_template:
Task: {{input.task}}

Artifact logical name (must match create step): {{input.artifact_name}}

1) Call `load_artifact` with name "{{input.artifact_name}}" and version 0 (latest).
2) Call `append_artifact` with the same name and `data` set to a UTF-8 string
   containing EXACTLY one new line, with no extra lines:
   {{input.append_line}}

3) Reply with two lines: SNIPPET=<first 100 chars of text from load>  APPEND=done
